database.query: SELECT START_005 as start, STOP_006 as STOP, TRAN_001 as TRAN, CPUTIME, ELAPSED , USERID_089 as user,DB2REQCT_180 as db2req,abcodec_114 as abend_code, netuowsx_098 as netid,netuowpx_097 as netsname from CR00515.EPQ110_1_TRXACCT where SYSTEM='SIES' and START_005_DATE=?' and TRAN_001=? and CPUTIME BETWEEN ? and ?;
